author: Epic Games
description:
HADES II v1.0 is OUT NOW!!
Battle beyond the Underworld vs. the Titan of Time in the bewitching sequel to the award-winning god-like rogue-like from Supergiant Games.
Whether you've been playing all through Early Access or this will be your very first foray into the Underworld of Greek myth, it's the perfect night to dive in! Now on the Epic Games Store: https://epic.gm/hades2
title: Hades II | Version 1.0 Launch
